Assay Development Educational Series

Overview

January 12, 2016

Motivation

  • Reports of analytical validation in BRC submissions are often deficient
  • Clinical researchers dont give much attention to the biomarker assay and how well it needs to perform

Goals

Educate clinical researchers on importance of assessing and reporting on the performance of assays.

Vision

  • Write a series of short lessons that illustrate the key concepts
  • Develop content agnostic to the delivery method (text-based and source figures)
    • In a structured and standardized format
    • Using diverse expertise across the program
  • Deliver as a webpage as user-guided curriculum
    • Short courses
    • Tutorial Papers
    • Videos

Statistical Issues in Biomarker-Based Clinical Trial Design
